{"tid":852660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹看演唱會　驚見男女「金槍撞鐘」做愛","createTime":"2018-10-08T04:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T04:51:10.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cff610839c86686e88ea41b29e8e5fa8a9866b3e","tid":852660,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"巴西「 Governador Magalhaes Pinto」體育館近日正在舉行一場音樂祭演唱會，但被現場參加演唱會的群眾拍到，一對男女直接在觀眾席上做愛，更挑戰「金槍撞鐘」等性姿勢<br />\n。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，畫面可見現場正在進行演唱會，不時響起電音的動感節奏，還有一名正妹與男友正在欣賞音樂，頭部也跟著節奏擺動。但就在這群觀眾的後方觀眾席，還有一對男女，呈現裸體姿態，男子更上演「金槍撞鐘」，臀部隨著電音節奏晃動，依照拍子撞上女子的下體，兩人還一度更換性姿勢，讓現場旁觀的群眾為之驚嘆。<br />\n <br />\n不過主辦音樂會的「OTM」製作公司表示，已經掌握到這對野戰男女的身分，並已報警，相信這對男女將會為此行為付出代價。根據巴西法律，野外露出猥褻恐被判有期徒刑3個月到1年。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"7c38ffb323f33121ab18478fed0b2c95e32e2596","tid":852660,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"屌唔google唔知有呢招"},{"pid":"ea26fe7642ff6b769f61bba98185012f1ddf5e45","tid":852660,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"c7e20308d42691a8e30263215e3e242b96703e49","tid":852660,"uid":34295,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181007/1442907/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181007%2F1442907%2F&d=GnYOVBWD5ThRqoI9%2BJHumb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3936eec3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181007%2F1442907%2F&h=66185bfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181007/1442907/</a><br />\n<br />\n救樓主老母"},{"pid":"adb6043c336e293e556a56920761c63770546ec3","tid":852660,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"搵唔到資料，點樣係金槍撞鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a